A black box system is when we do not know how works a system.
Functions can be black boxes because you gonna use functions that you did not create but you do not know what is inside.
What is important is to know when and how to use it.

Activity:
Write down three things that you interact with on a daily basis even though you cannot explain how they work.

1) The air conditioning system.
2) The microwave.
3) How the tv displays content to the channels.
